This product includes software and documentation developed for the
qingming-stark-g64 project.

QINGMING-STARK-G64 provides a reproducible CLI-based QSPG64 STARK proving
and verification backend verified on AMD RX 7900 XTX 24GB.

The official integration surface is:
  - CLI prover
  - QSPG64 .qsp proof file
  - standalone verifier

This baseline intentionally does not provide:
  - libqingming_stark_g64.so
  - official C ABI
  - official C++ SDK
  - Rust crate
  - Python package
  - black-box binary SDK

